  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the intraocular pressure-lowering effect and the
      safety of DE-117 ophthalmic solution compared with Latanoprost ophthalmic solution in
      subjects with open angle glaucoma or ocular hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
